flowchart LR
    U[Researcher] --> FX[JavaFX Viewer / PatternFinder]
    FX --> TASK[Java Task and executor controllers]
    TASK --> DBJ[Java cache and database adapters]
    DBJ --> JNA[JNA Wrapper]
    JNA --> CABI[C exports in wrapper.cpp]
    CABI --> ALG[C++ code / unfolding / equations / refinement]
    CABI <--> SQL[(SQLite pool)]
    ALG --> TBB[TBB and Boost worker stages]
    CABI --> OWN[Native result allocation]
    OWN --> JNA
    JNA --> COPY[Java copy then native cleanup]
    COPY --> COMMIT[Generation-checked JavaFX commit]
    COMMIT --> U
